@startuml
title Adapter - Ejemplo 2 - solucion para API externa incompatible
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class CrmCustomerAdapter {
    +findCustomer(String id): Customer
  }
  class Customer {
    +toString(): String
  }
  interface CustomerProvider <<interfaz>> {
  }
  class ExternalCrmApi {
    +getCustomerXml(String id): String
  }
}

CustomerProvider <|.. CrmCustomerAdapter
CrmCustomerAdapter ..> Customer : crea
CustomerProvider ..> Customer : crea
ExternalCrmApi ..> Customer : crea
Main ..> CrmCustomerAdapter : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
